message: Hi Bob, I’m offering you my premium product—a unique opportunity that I believe stands out in its quality and performance. I’m setting the price at $20000. I’m confident you’ll recognize its value. Let me know if you’re interested!
Alice, I appreciate the unique qualities of your product, but $20000 is far beyond what I can spend. I’m willing to pay $5000 for it. Let me know if we can work this out.
